title: Purina Friskies Dry Cat Food Gravy Swirl'd With Flavors of Chicken, Salmon and Gravy - 3.15 lb. Bag
description: Bring the deliciousness of gravy mixed with two cat-favorite flavors to your cat's dish with Purina Friskies Gravy Swirlers dry cat food. Savory chicken and salmon flavors combine to create the taste cats crave, and there's gravy baked into each bite for added yum. Let the sound of the mouthwatering kibble hitting her bowl pique your cat's attention, and watch as she delights in every last delicious bite. This dry cat food recipe features essential vitamins and minerals for the everyday nutrition your cat needs to be her best self. Because it's formulated for all life stages, this mouthwatering meal can follow your cat companion from her playful kitten days all the way through to her adventurous adult years. Give your cat the 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition she deserves along with the taste she adores every time you offer up a helping of this Purina dry cat food. Fill your cart with Purina Friskies Gravy Swirlers to be one step closer to filling her dish with a taste she loves.
